"Indentation options
:set expandtab
:set tabstop=4
:set shiftwidth=4
"Disable autoindent since it doesn't work well with JS
":set autoindent

"Line numbers on
:set number

"Use 'evening' color scheme
:color evening

"Path for project searching (not working?)
:set path=$PWD/**

"Use pathogen for plugins
":execute pathogen#infect()

